name: August10.wad
description: A level for DEATHMATCH only! Lots o'mazes is the keyword for this level! Play it with DEATHMATCH 1.0 or DEATHMATCH 2.0 rules... that's up to you. All weapons are available on skill 3/4/5, no BFG on skill 1/2. It's quite dark and sinister so be careful and watch your back!
